All Implemented Interfaces:
Type
public class SimpleType
extends Component
implements Type

Encapsulates an atomic simple type. Simple types define the data type using the base attribute. The value of the base attribute is either a xsd type or another simple type. If the base attribute is absent, the data type may be defined by creating an inline simple type inside the simple type.

If a simple type definition has as its parent, then the scope is global; otherwise the scope is local.

Currently the list and union types are not supported. Only restriction is supported.
